{"tid":2494373,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"一條關於Array既問題","createTime":"2021-04-18T14:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T15:42:16.000Z","uid":257658,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2893d601a453c50978ceabee01e18f2c44294aff","tid":2494373,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的. 我用C++寫緊個Inventory System.<br />\n好似生化危機咁樣. 可以inspect, use item, drop item... etc.<br />\nInventory用一條array儲著.<br />\n科興就係Inventory[0], inventory[1],[2],[3] ....<br />\nExample: <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRUAFJKE5Svn31Uvj3gEBR4UvugY8u7bhZzmXzGZSBmVC?filename=baYvjXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaYvjXb.png&h=bc31dca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本隻驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaUFQ4XQV1emt8L1J47AbmiCmBfaYzm3UKLLWeze3kTa1?filename=KEJbOPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEJbOPW.png&h=16ecc58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來都就黎寫完. 但岩岩玩玩RE Village先唸起.<br />\nItem既位置可以隨意調換. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/unexpected.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n但點樣做到佢上下左右調Item果個效果?<br />\nE.g. GIF:<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWgsVjZg8rvd8DuDznUWkJyEtNBRiQsBArbw2LoVmEmn1?filename=8coZXHE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8coZXHE.gif&h=79f90471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係我既approach已經係錯左? 原本隻驚唔係用array儲inventory item?"},{"pid":"8f20ba6131456830324f652ffe95c019f6072b90","tid":2494373,"uid":46200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"就咁swap 未得？有咩特別？"},{"pid":"1f353ba826e07e7957feb4bf9b6112913c30e076","tid":2494373,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"用pointer"},{"pid":"13e8e3704428230b791bf567f0aa967b2eaab4e6","tid":2494373,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04